    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it is very sound; the engine starts reliably every time, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. The interior is clean with only minor signs of use, and the exterior paint retains a nice shine, though you may find a few small, typical stone chips upon close inspection. It is a dependable car that is ready for its next owner to drive home with confidence.",
