    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey friends! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total showstopper! This car is in truly flawless condition\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept and pampered every single day. It honestly feels and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. You won\u2019t find a single blemish on it! I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
